@node "Présentation" "Overview"
@next "Installation"
@prev "Main"
@{b}@{u}Overview@{ub}@{uu}

 BExchange is just a replacement for the  workbench commodity 'Exchange'.
 It's a commodity manager.

 Features:

    o Uses the bgui.library
    o Resizeable
    o Keyboard shortcup for listview and buttons
    o Keyboard shortcuts for listview and buttons
    o Opens its GUI on the active screen
    o Can do actions on all commodities
@endnode

@node "Installation" "Installation"
@next "Paramčtres"
@prev "Présentation"
@{b}@{u}Installation@{ub}@{uu}

 Just click on the 'Install_English' icon and answer the questions.
@endnode

@node "Paramčtres" "Parameters"
@next "Interface"
@prev "Installation"
@{b}@{u}Parameters@{ub}@{uu}

 The parameters of BExchange can be modified with the tooltypes  of  its
 icon.

 @{u}GUI parameters@{uu}

    SimpleRefresh = YES         The window of BExchange will be in
                                SimpleRefresh mode

                    NO          The window will be in SmartRefresh mode



    Aspect =        THIN        Gadget frames will be in THIN mode

                    STANDARD    Gadget frames will be in THICK mode

                    AUTO        Gadget frames will be THIN or THICK
                                according to the screen aspect-ratio


    Frame =         STANDARD    Gadget frames look normal

                    XEN         Gadget frames will be in XEN mode


    NEWLOOKSCROLLER YES         The scroller of the listview will have
                                the newlook (white).

                    NO          The scroller will have the normal look
                                (black).


    MINENTRIES      <nombre>    To specify how many entries should be
                                visible at all times (min=3).


    PUBSCREEN       <Ecran>     Name of a pubscreen for open window on it.



    WINDOWPOSITION  CENTERSCREEN    The window will be opened on the center
                                    of the screen.

                    CENTERMOUSE     The window will be opened on the mouse.

                    TOPLEFT         The window will be opened on the top left
                                    of the screen.


    SCALEWIDTH      <nombre>        Width in percentage of the window compared
                                    to its mininum width.


    SCALEHEIGHT     <nombre>        Width in percentage of the window compared
                                    to its minimum height.


 @{u}Commodity parameters@{uu}


    CX_POPUP =      YES         Open its window when first started

    CX_POPKEY =     <hotkey>    Hotkey
                                (default: 'control help')

    CX_PRIORITY =   0           Priority of the hotkey
@endnode

@node "Interface" "GUI"
@next "Menus"
@prev "Paramčtres"
@{b}@{u}GUI@{ub}@{uu}


 @{u}o Buttons@{uu}

    These buttons are available when a commodity is selected.


    @{bg fill}Show Interface    @{bg back}            Ask the selected commodity to show
                                  its GUI.
                                  (KeyBoard: ENTER)

    @{bg fill}Hide Interface    @{bg back}            Ask the commodity to hide its GUI.


    @{bg fill}Active/Inactive   @{bg back}            Enable or disable the commodity or
                                  its Hotkeys.
                                  (KeyBoard: SPACE)

    @{bg fill}Remove            @{bg back}            Ask the commodity to quit.
                                  (KeyBoard: DELETE)


  @{b}@{bg fill}Hide                @{ub}@{bg back}            Hide the window of BExchange.

  @{b}@{bg fill}Quit                @{ub}@{bg back}            Quit BExchange.
@endnode

@node "Menus" "Menus"
@next "Désistement"
@prev "Interface"
@{b}@{u}Menus@{ub}@{uu}


    @{bg fill}Projet@{bg back}
         @{bg fill} @{bg back}               
        @{bg fill}About...@{bg back}            Open a requester that gives information about
         @{bg fill} @{bg back}                  BExchange     
        @{bg fill}Hide  @{bg back}              Hide the GUI of BExchange
         @{bg fill} @{bg back}       
        @{bg fill}Quit @{bg back}               Quit BExchange :-(


    @{bg fill}Tools@{bg back}
        @{bg fill} @{bg back}                
        @{bg fill}Show all      @{bg back}      Show GUI of all commodities.
        @{bg fill} @{bg back}                  
        @{bg fill}Hide all      @{bg back}      Hide GUI of all commodities.
        @{bg fill} @{bg back}                  
        @{bg fill} @{bg back}                     
        @{bg fill}Activate all  @{bg back}      Activate all commodities.
        @{bg fill} @{bg back}                     
        @{bg fill}Deactivate all@{bg back}      Deactivate all commodities.
        @{bg fill} @{bg back}                  
        @{bg fill} @{bg back}                       
        @{bg fill}Remove all    @{bg back}      Remove all commodities.
@endnode

