@{b}@{u}License@{ub}@{uu}

 BExchange is freely distributable as long as NO MODIFICATION  is  made  to
 the program or the package. It may NOT be distributed without its package.

 It may be distributed in PD collections, on servers, networks or on CD-ROM.


 BExchange is GIFTWARE, this means that if you like it you should send me
 something like:

  - Net-mail, financial-contribution, post card, programs,  felicitations,
    A4000T..


 It's a complete version, no limitations :-)

 Commercial usage is prohibited without the agreement of the @{"author" link "Author" 0}.
@endnode

