@node "Historique" "History"
@next "A faire..."
@prev "Remerciements"
@{b}@{u}History@{ub}@{uu}

 @{u} Version    Date         Description                                      @{uu}

    1.0      (8.6.95)     First version

    1.1      (25.7.95)    Added a shortcut (SPACE) for
                          activate/deactivate commodities.
                          Suggested by Alain Valleton.

                          Added double click and return key
                          for show interface of commodities.
                          Suggested by Nick Christie.

                          Added options: NEWLOOKSCROLLER, MINENTRIES,
                          PUBSCREEN.
                          Suggested by Nick Christie.

                          Added options: WINDOWPOSITIN, SCALEWIDTH,
                          SCALEHEIGHT.

    1.2      (25.1.96)    Small bug with the scroller.

                          Now information will be centered.

                          Modification of ToolType SMARTREFRESH to
                          SIMPLEREFRESH.

                          New ToolType NoBufferRP, it will speed display
                          under RTG when set to "YES".
@endnode

